01:48.467 --> 01:52.467
-Man (over radio):
Towards the Shop Rite,
he's southbound on University.

01:52.500 --> 01:54.233
-He's southbound
in the northbound lanes

01:54.267 --> 01:56.567
on University.
I'll call it out, Mike.

01:56.600 --> 01:58.467
-Man (over radio):
I'm gonna back off
a little bit, Asher.

01:58.500 --> 02:00.467
He's back in his lane now.

02:02.067 --> 02:04.433
-I think your buddy
just bailed.
-Reaux: He's bailin'.

02:04.467 --> 02:06.167
-Yeah, he just bailed.

02:06.200 --> 02:08.367
-(siren continues)
-(radio chatter)

02:08.400 --> 02:10.333
-Man (over radio):
Okay, this is good, Pete.

02:15.600 --> 02:18.233
-(sirens wailing)

02:18.267 --> 02:20.733
-He's runnin' that way!

02:20.767 --> 02:24.167
-(radio chatter)
-(sirens continue)

02:25.467 --> 02:28.067
(sirens wailing)

02:29.067 --> 02:31.867
-(panting)

02:31.900 --> 02:35.300
-If he was goin'
through the yards,
