02:35.333 --> 02:37.067
-Man (over radio):
He's running on Madeleine!

02:37.067 --> 02:38.600
(radio chatter)

02:38.633 --> 02:40.067
We're trying to block
him in now.

02:40.067 --> 02:42.333
We got a uniform at Joan
and a uniform at Madeleine.

02:42.367 --> 02:45.067
We need somebody to get
to First Street on Madeleine,

02:45.100 --> 02:47.667
east of, uh,
east of... (indistinct)

02:47.700 --> 02:49.900
-We're at Madeleine
and Popler.

02:49.933 --> 02:51.900
Mike's back at, uh, University.

02:51.933 --> 02:56.067
-(barking)
-(indistinct radio chatter)

02:56.067 --> 02:58.233
-They're gonna be doin'
a K-9 track.

02:59.667 --> 03:01.933
-Like I said, police K-9!
Come on out! Identify yourself!

03:01.967 --> 03:04.100
Or this police dog,
he will bite!

03:04.133 --> 03:05.967
(speaks indistinctly)

